text: Kildonan-River East is a future provincial electoral district in the Canadian province of Manitoba that will come into effect at the 2019 Manitoba general election. It will elect one member to the Legislative Assembly of Manitoba. The riding was created by the 2018 provincial redistribution out of parts of Kildonan, River East and a small part of St. Johns.
